  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a randomized controlled trial to examine the impact of two brief interventions on
      adolescent and young adult alcohol use behaviors. The interventions being compared are
      motivational interviewing (MI) and brief adolescent mindfulness (BAM).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
